        Parameters:
        newCountry - Country node whose neighbors are required.
        newPlayer - player who owns the required neighbours.
        flag - if true, method returns countries owned by newPlayer, if false return countries owned by other players except newPlayer.
        Returns:
        playerNeighbouringCountries returns neighbouring countries of the country of same owner
